name: Twilight Seraphina Sovereign
text: Ascended from the fabled Seraphina, the Sovereign now reigns, her crystalline fur casting prismatic light across the glades. Majestic, she soars, her arcane horn an eternal compass through realms unseen. The enchanted forest bows to her evolved grace, her diamond teeth a testament to her enduring dominion in the stars.

The unicorn's teeth have metamorphized into almost see-through, diamond-like incisors. This unicorn, bearing a sense of aristocracy, navigates through a mesmerizing sky full of swirling auroras and shooting stars.
